22:1 COMMENT "# A record with a user-defined `create` that takes a single seed and"
22:69 EOL "\n"
23:1 COMMENT "# derives both fields from it. The body uses `meta.create` -- the internal"
23:75 EOL "\n"
24:1 COMMENT "# raw allocator of the enclosing type -- to set the final field values."
24:72 EOL "\n"
25:1 COMMENT "# Calling `myrec` as a constructor (bare-name or explicit `.create`) now"
25:73 EOL "\n"
26:1 COMMENT "# routes through this user function."
26:37 EOL "\n"
